{"parentUuid":"15f81b5e-32d2-4a75-836f-417ac30936e6","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"adb9276692a3e70f3","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01MT9VL1uBBeuAzzA9tCtqHN","type":"tool_result","content":"<persisted-output>\nOutput too large (52.8KB). Full output saved to: /Users/dhyana/.claude/projects/-Users-dhyana/2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75/tool-results/toolu_01MT9VL1uBBeuAzzA9tCtqHN.txt\n\nPreview (first 2KB):\n     1→# Jagat Kalyan: Partner Research Document\n     2→\n     3→**Version**: 2026-03-11 | **Status**: Actionable Research Brief\n     4→**Author**: Compiled via deep web research across 6 partner categories\n     5→\n     6→---\n     7→\n     8→## The Jagat Kalyan Loop\n     9→\n    10→```\n    11→AI Companies fund carbon offsets\n    12→        |\n    13→        v\n    14→Ecological Restoration Projects\n    15→        |\n    16→        v\n    17→Employ AI-Displaced Workers (just transition)\n    18→        |\n    19→        v\n    20→AI Tools Scale Impact (MRV, monitoring, optimization)\n    21→        |\n    22→        v\n    23→Verified Welfare-Tons Attract More Funding\n    24→        |\n    25→        +-----------> Loop closes, scales\n    26→```\n    27→\n    28→---\n    29→\n    30→## Architecture: How Partners Map to the JK Loop\n    31→\n    32→```\n    33→                         JAGAT KALYAN PARTNER ECOSYSTEM\n    34→  ============================================================================\n    35→\n    36→  FUNDING LAYER (Who pays)\n    37→  +------------------------------------------------------------------+\n    38→  |  Microsoft ($793M+ climate tech) | Amazon (Climate Pledge)       |\n    39→  |  Google (net-zero 2030)          | Anthropic (Econ Futures $10M) |\n    40→  |  Meta (net-zero 2030)            | OpenAI (via Azure green infra)|\n    41→  +------------------------------------------------------------------+\n    42→           |                                          |\n    43→           | Carbon credit                            | Workforce\n    44→           | purchases                                | transition\n    45→           v                                          v grants\n    46→  MARKET LAYER (How value flows)          WORKFORCE LAYER (Who benefits)\n    47→  +-------------------------------+       +------------------------------+\n    48→  | Verra (VCS registry)          |       | Anthropic Econ Futures       |\n...\n</persisted-output>"}]},"uuid":"61b6e026-cf22-408b-bb80-5f4f6a8cb113","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:20:26.980Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"15f81b5e-32d2-4a75-836f-417ac30936e6","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
