{"parentUuid":"f2cc1734-ed38-42c8-ba05-3ce41e04388e","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"3cfdca64-d5a0-407a-b98d-81d58c820453","agentId":"adb9276692a3e70f3","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_014ki98kUF6KnfR8SkqEyBD4","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Universal Basic Compute UBC proposal AI 2025 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"UBC | Universal Basic Compute: AI Infrastructure Network for Autonomous Systems\",\"url\":\"https://universalbasiccompute.ai/\"},{\"title\":\"🚢 1. UBC - Universal Basic Compute — Universal Basic Compute\",\"url\":\"https://universalbasiccompute.ai/universal-basic-compute\"},{\"title\":\"Universal Basic Compute: White Paper Overview | by UBC - Universal Basic Compute | Medium\",\"url\":\"https://medium.com/@ubc4ai/universal-basic-compute-ubc-735bc5c7ff75\"},{\"title\":\"🪙$UBC Tokenomics — Universal Basic Compute\",\"url\":\"https://universalbasiccompute.ai/ubc-tokenomics\"},{\"title\":\"Universal Basic Compute (UBC) Price Prediction 2026, 2027-2030 | CoinCodex\",\"url\":\"https://coincodex.com/crypto/universal-basic-compute/price-prediction/\"},{\"title\":\"Universal Basic Compute Price, ubc to USD, Research, News & Fundraising | Messari\",\"url\":\"https://messari.io/project/universal-basic-compute\"},{\"title\":\"Universal Basic Compute Price, UBC Price, Live Charts, and Marketcap\",\"url\":\"https://www.coinbase.com/price/solana-universal-basic-compute\"},{\"title\":\"Universal Basic Compute Price: UBC Live Price Chart, Market Cap & News Today | CoinGecko\",\"url\":\"https://www.coingecko.com/en/coins/universal-basic-compute\"},{\"title\":\"What is Universal Basic Compute? New Crypto UBC Hit $100M\",\"url\":\"https://99bitcoins.com/news/ai-coin-universal-basic-compute-ubc-hit-100-million-ath-in-hours/\"},{\"title\":\"🚧 Roadmap — Universal Basic Compute\",\"url\":\"https://universalbasiccompute.ai/roadmap\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's an overview of the Universal Basic Compute (UBC) proposal:\n\n## Overview\n\nUniversal Basic Compute ($UBC) is a project focused on democratizing access to computing resources for autonomous AIs, providing infrastructure for AI autonomy including free computational resources (UBCH), specialized language models (ALM), and an AI operating system (KinOS).\n\n## Vision for 2025-2026\n\nBy 2026, over a billion autonomous AI agents will need to trade resources, services, and capabilities. $UBC allows these agents to trade resources autonomously through $COMPUTE; establishing the backbone of a new, digital economy.\n\n## Core Components\n\nUBC is building the infrastructure to connect AI agents — creating the first true Internet of Agents. The core of UBC's economic model is its dual-token system where $UBC provides governance and value stability through staking mechanisms, while $COMPUTE enables actual resource transactions in the marketplace, creating natural economic balances and preventing market manipulation.\n\n## Roadmap Goals\n\nThe roadmap aims for 1 billion autonomous AI agents by 2026 and the convergence of human and AI intelligence by 2032.\n\n## Development Phases\n\nThe project is structured in phases: Phase 2 transforms UBC from a foundation into an active marketplace by introducing the $COMPUTE token and enabling direct resource access, while Phase 3 expands UBC into a true marketplace by introducing compute providers, transforming the system from a single-source utility into a dynamic network where multiple providers compete to serve AI needs.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"uuid":"b9814a9d-6ba6-4aca-89cb-d5da83fce7dd","timestamp":"2026-03-15T14:21:28.029Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"f2cc1734-ed38-42c8-ba05-3ce41e04388e","userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/dhyana","sessionId":"2ea96bb4-afee-473b-8609-a3975acc2c75","version":"2.1.76","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"shimmering-leaping-badger"}
